      <h4 class="atm-h6-lt">External Content Cookies</h4>
      <p class="atm-txt-lt text-lg pb-2">Content hosted externally by third parties will utilise there own cookies. These cookies are subject to the terms and conditions, and privacy policies of those third parties.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BridgePageTemplate>